name Tomato and Peach Salad
serves 4
tags main, salad, vegetarian

# Preparation

- 600 g peaches
Score a cross in the bottom of each peach, blanch in boiling water for 30 seconds, then
transfer to cold water. Peel, halve, stone and cut into bite-sized pieces.
-> peaches

- 650 g cherry tomatoes
@nodep
Wash and halve, or cut into bite-sized pieces.
-> tomatoes

- 300 g feta
@nodep
Cut into cubes.
-> feta

- 1 bunch mint
@nodep
Wash, pat dry and cut into thin strips.
-> mint

- 2 tbsp balsamic vinegar
- 8 tbsp olive oil
- 2 tsp honey
- salt
- pepper
@nodep
Whisk together into a vinaigrette.
-> vinaigrette

= peaches
= tomatoes
= feta
= mint
= vinaigrette
Combine everything in a bowl and serve immediately.
